content.title: Add a Collection
content.body:
1. From the main menu, navigate to Project > Import > Component into Library.
    The file explorer opens.
  2. Navigate to the UI collection download location and select the zip file.
  3. Click Open.
    The Import Marketplace Item window appears.
  4. Fill in the following details.
    Library Name: NFIcollections
    Collection Name: BarcodeScanner

You can view the added UI collection in the My Libraries tab.
